Kinetimancers are force-manipulation casters who redirect momentum rather than generating power from nothing.
They synthesize Necromancer (Entropy Scholar) and Egomancer (Assertion Wing) methodologies through shared momentum mechanics.
The tradition arose from the Kinetic Formulists, who found mathematical analogies between psionic will-imposition and entropic force propagation.
Core doctrine: all effective force operates through redirection of existing momentum, not generation of new force.
Combat role is counter-attacker and force redirector. Incoming attacks become resources for the practitioner.
Signature technique: Kinetic Reversion, which reverses incoming force vectors back toward their origin.
More powerful attacks are more useful to a Kinetimancer, inverting normal threat logic.
This is a remort class combining psionic and entropic disciplines.
Practitioners are few, independent, and technically sophisticated. Registry oversight has never been effectively implemented.
The Violet Compact classified the tradition as dangerous synthesis and assigned the bureaucratic label that became its name.
